conds'''&nbsp;\u2013 {{flagicon|CHI}} [[Iv\u00e1n Zamorano]] v [[Sevilla FC]], [[1994\u201395 La Liga]], 3 September 1994<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.marca.com/deporte/futbol/2012/goles-rapidos/ |title=Los goles m\u00e1s r\u00e1pidos de la liga |publisher=MARCA.com |date= |accessdate=25 September 2013}}</ref>\n**'''14 seconds'''&nbsp;\u2013 {{flagicon|BRA}} [[Ronaldo (Brazilian footballer)|Ronaldo]] v [[Atl\u00e9tico Madrid]], [[2003\u201304 La Liga]], 3 December 2003<ref>{{cite web|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2003/SPORT/football/12/03/spain.real/ |title=Quickfire Ronaldo proves Real hero |publisher=Edition.cnn.com |date= |accessdate=25 September 2013}}</ref>\n* Fastest [[hat-trick]]: '''8 minutes'''\n**{{flagicon|ESP|1945}} [[Jos\u00e9 Garc\u00eda Castro|Pepillo II]] v [[Real Sociedad]], [[1959\u201360 La Liga]], 10 April 1960<ref name=\"leyendablanca.galeon.com\">{{cite web|url=http://leyendablanca.galeon.com/tempo60.htm |title=Temporada 1959\u201360 |publisher=Leyendablanca.galeon.com |date= |accessdate=25 September 2013}}</ref>\n**{{flagicon|POR}} [[Cristiano Ronaldo]] v [[Granada CF|Granada]], [[2014\u201315 La Liga]], 5 April 2015\n* Fastest four goals: '''20 minutes'''&nbsp;\u2013 {{flagicon|POR}} [[Cristiano Ronaldo]] v [[Malm\u00f6 FF]], [[2015\u201316 UEFA Champions League]], 8 December 2015\n* Fastest five goals: ''' 39 minutes'''&nbsp;\u2013 {{flagicon|ESP|1945}} [[Jos\u00e9 Garc\u00eda Castro|Pepillo II]] v [[Elche CF]], [[1959\u201360 La Liga]], 7 February 1960<ref name=\"leyendablanca.galeon.com\" />\n* Most hat-tricks in all competitions: '''44'''&nbsp;\u2013 {{flagicon|POR}} [[Cristiano Ronaldo]], 2009\u20132018\n* Most hat-tricks in [[La Liga]]: '''34'''&nbsp;\u2013 {{flagicon|POR}} [[Cristiano Ronaldo]], 2009\u20132018\n* Most hat-tricks in a single season: '''8'''&nbsp;\u2013 {{flagicon|POR}} [[Cristiano Ronaldo]], 2014\u201315 (All in La Liga\u2013once with four goals and once with five goals)\n\n==== Historical goals ====\n{| class=\"wikitable