ws |url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/28926665 |title=Angel Di Maria: Man Utd pay British record \u00a359.7m for winger| publisher=BBC Sport}}</ref>\n|-\n|3||{{flagicon|ESP}} [[\u00c1lvaro Morata]]||{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Chelsea F.C.|Chelsea]]||\u00a358||\u20ac65.5||July 2017||<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.chelseafc.com/news/latest-news/2017/07/morata-is-a-blue.html\n|title=Morata is a Blue  |date=21 July 2017 |accessdate=22 July 2017 |work=chelseafc.com}}</ref>\n|-\n|4||{{flagicon|GER}} [[Mesut \u00d6zil]]||{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Arsenal F.C.|Arsenal]]||\u00a342.5||\u20ac50||September 2013||<ref name=\"Mesut Ozil: Arsenal sign Real Madrid midfielder for \u00a342.5m\">{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/23929339 |title=Mesut Ozil: Arsenal sign Real Madrid midfielder for \u00a342.5m |date=2 September 2013|accessdate=8 September 2013 |publisher=BBC Sport}}</ref>\n|-\n|5||{{flagicon|CRO}} [[Mateo Kovacic]]||{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Chelsea F.C.|Chelsea]]||\u00a340.3||\u20ac45||July 2019||<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.givemesport.com/1486854-mateo-kovacic-completes-45-million-move-from-real-madrid-to-chelsea |date=21 July 2018 |accessdate=2 July 2019 |work=givemesport.com}}</ref>\n|-\n|6||{{flagicon|BRA}} [[Robinho]]||{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Manchester City F.C.|Manchester City]]||\u00a332.5||\u20ac42||September 2008||<ref name=\"Robinho to complete \u00a332.5m Man City move\">{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/7593026.stm |title=Man City beat Chelsea to Robinho |date=1 September 2008|accessdate=8 August 2013 |publisher=BBC Sport}}</ref>\n|-\n|7||{{flagicon|ARG}} [[Gonzalo Higua\u00edn]]||{{flagicon|ITA}} [[S.S.C. Napoli|Napoli]]||\u00a334.5||\u20ac40||July 2013||<ref name=\"Higua\u00edn: Real Madrid striker completes move to Napoli\">{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/23442542 |title=Gonzalo Higua\u00edn: Real Madrid striker completes move to Napoli |date=27 July 2013|accessdate=8 August 2013 